    <entry>
      <title>AE 让光书写文字</title>
      <link href="/2018/08/23/loli/"/>
      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="这是一篇AEの教学"><a href="#这是一篇AEの教学" class="headerlink" title="这是一篇AEの教学"></a>这是一篇AEの教学</h3><a id="more"></a><h3 id="制作本效果需要如下插件"><a href="#制作本效果需要如下插件" class="headerlink" title="制作本效果需要如下插件"></a>制作本效果需要如下插件</h3><p>Optical Flares<br><a href="https://pan.baidu.com/s/1AUeHFfHaaPRZcMEzmnndJw" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>下载地址</strong></a><br>25am</p><hr><p>首先打开AE建立一个loli的5s合成<br><img src="http://139.196.127.74/kdy/data/User/admin/home/loli/Snipaste_2018-08-23_19-16-08.png" alt=""></p><p>输入文字“loli”</p><p><img src="http://139.196.127.74/kdy/data/User/admin/home/loli/Snipaste_2018-08-23_19-24-05.png" alt=""></p><p>利用从文字创建蒙版做出轮廓</p><p><img src="http://139.196.127.74/kdy/data/User/admin/home/loli/ps.png" alt=""></p><p>给蒙版层添加字体描边效果</p><p><img src="http://139.196.127.74/kdy/data/User/admin/home/loli/Snipaste_2018-08-23_19-26-40.png" alt=""></p><p>勾选所有蒙版取消勾选顺序描边</p><p><img src="http://139.196.127.74/kdy/data/User/admin/home/loli/Snipaste_2018-08-23_19-28-23.png" alt=""></p><p>这时候拉动结束选项进度条就会看到不发光的效果了</p><p><img src="/images/placeholder.png" alt="" data-src="http://139.196.127.74/kdy/data/User/admin/home/loli/Snipaste_2018-08-23_19-40-10.png" class="lazyload"></p><p>接下来</p><h4 id="使文字发光"><a href="#使文字发光" class="headerlink" title="使文字发光"></a>使文字发光</h4><hr><p>我们新建控制层快捷键Ctrl+Shift+Alt+Y<br>将loli蒙版L下的蒙版路径复制然后粘贴在新建控制层的位置下快捷键P(一定是P下而不是控制层下)</p><p><img src="/images/placeholder.png" alt="" data-src="http://139.196.127.74/kdy/data/User/admin/home/loli/Snipaste_2018-08-23_19-43-13.png" class="lazyload"></p><p>调节位置结束时间大概在快结束之前</p><p><img src="/images/placeholder.png" alt="" data-src="http://139.196.127.74/kdy/data/User/admin/home/loli/Snipaste_2018-08-23_19-43-29.png" class="lazyload"><br><img src="/images/placeholder.png" alt="" data-src="http://139.196.127.74/kdy/data/User/admin/home/loli/Snipaste_2018-08-23_19-43-47.png" class="lazyload"></p><p>新建纯色Ctrl+Y(颜色随意)</p><p><img src="/images/placeholder.png" alt="" data-src="http://139.196.127.74/kdy/data/User/admin/home/loli/Snipaste_2018-08-23_19-44-47.png" class="lazyload"></p><p>在效果里选择安装的Optical Flares插件</p><p><img src="/images/placeholder.png" alt="" data-src="http://139.196.127.74/kdy/data/User/admin/home/loli/Snipaste_2018-08-23_19-45-01.png" class="lazyload"></p><p>点击设置更改光源效果颜色等等凭自己喜好并调整光源大小以适应文字的边线</p><p><img src="/images/placeholder.png" alt="" data-src="http://139.196.127.74/kdy/data/User/admin/home/loli/Snipaste_2018-08-23_19-45-16.png" class="lazyload"><br><img src="/images/placeholder.png" alt="" data-src="http://139.196.127.74/kdy/data/User/admin/home/loli/Snipaste_2018-08-23_19-46-29.png" class="lazyload"></p><p>渲染模式调为透明混合模式改为相加</p><p><img src="/images/placeholder.png" alt="" data-src="http://139.196.127.74/kdy/data/User/admin/home/loli/Snipaste_2018-08-23_19-47-50.png" class="lazyload"><br><img src="/images/placeholder.png" alt="" data-src="http://139.196.127.74/kdy/data/User/admin/home/loli/Snipaste_2018-08-23_19-48-08.png" class="lazyload"></p><p>按住Alt点击位置xy做蚊香线连接到控制层到位置xy上</p><p><img src="/images/placeholder.png" alt="" data-src="http://139.196.127.74/kdy/data/User/admin/home/loli/Snipaste_2018-08-23_19-48-38.png" class="lazyload"><br><img src="/images/placeholder.png" alt="" data-src="http://139.196.127.74/kdy/data/User/admin/home/loli/Snipaste_2018-08-23_19-48-53.png" class="lazyload"></p><p>将控制层到3D开启并同时开启光源效果到3D</p><p><img src="/images/placeholder.png" alt="" data-src="http://139.196.127.74/kdy/data/User/admin/home/loli/Snipaste_2018-08-23_19-49-39.png" class="lazyload"></p><p>蚊香线连接Z轴</p><p><img src="/images/placeholder.png" alt="" data-src="http://139.196.127.74/kdy/data/User/admin/home/loli/Snipaste_2018-08-23_19-49-51.png" class="lazyload"></p><p>制作一个不透明度的效果使之达到缓慢出现的效果</p><p><img src="/images/placeholder.png" alt="" data-src="http://139.196.127.74/kdy/data/User/admin/home/loli/Snipaste_2018-08-23_20-11-55.png" class="lazyload"></p><p><strong>重复步骤</strong></p><hr><p>依次做出loli几个字母</p><p><img src="/images/placeholder.png" alt="" data-src="http://139.196.127.74/kdy/data/User/admin/home/loli/Snipaste_2018-08-23_20-12-25.png" class="lazyload"><br><img src="/images/placeholder.png" alt="" data-src="http://139.196.127.74/kdy/data/User/admin/home/loli/Snipaste_2018-08-23_20-23-40.png" class="lazyload"></p><p>做出后利用摄像机给整体添加动画</p><p><img src="/images/placeholder.png" alt="" data-src="http://139.196.127.74/kdy/data/User/admin/home/loli/Snipaste_2018-08-23_20-24-01.png" class="lazyload"></p><p>最后就可以渲染出炉啦</p><h3 id="最终效果演示"><a href="#最终效果演示" class="headerlink" title="最终效果演示"></a>最终效果演示</h3><div id="dplayer0" class="dplayer hexo-tag-dplayer-mark" style="margin-bottom: 20px;"></div><script>(function(){var player = new DPlayer({"container":document.getElementById("dplayer0"),"video":{"url":"http://139.196.127.74/kdy/data/User/admin/home/%E5%90%88%E6%88%90%201_2_1.mp4"}});window.dplayers||(window.dplayers=[]);window.dplayers.push(player);})()</script>]]></content>
      
      
